Everything seemed to move in slow motion as Shadow Wing hit the 
ground. she took the hit trying to help Lunarpine, He fealt a rage 
build, his first friend just go blown out of the sky. he didn't know 
how badly she was hurt, he just knew that she was lying on the ground 
leaking large amounts.

"YOU DID THIS TO HER YOU SON OF A CYBERDOG" The wolf had lost most of 
his self control as he lashed out at Ares. "I hope you have strong 
beliefs in the after function, you'll need it by the time I'm done."

his bold words echoed through the woods as the seemingly endless 
battle raged.
